    excerpt:
      "Palm Springs is home to the largest concentration of mid-century modern architecture in the world, and its ongoing preservation and adaptive reuse offer essential lessons for contemporary designers working in Southern California.",
    category: "socal-design",
    author: "IDI Editorial Team",
    publishedAt: "2026-02-07",
